title: Correction: Arena project funding
maintext: The story, “Arena seating project cost estimate goes down a half million,” in Wednesday’s Daily Record contained incorrect information about funding for the Ellensburg Rodeo Arena seating improvements. Kittitas County Commissioner Paul Jewell said the county is still working out the details for funding, and nothing has been approved yet by the county.
